{"type": "article", "id": 21126, "title": "调色桌", "description": "", "date": "2016-01-22T07:30:19Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 161922, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 25, "image": "img/article/article_show/2016060712230992rLVymFgXY6wfbB.jpeg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t西班牙设计师 Jaime Hayon 与丹麦设计品牌 &amp;tradition 合作频繁，这次科隆家具展上，他们带来了桌子和灯。palette desk(调色桌)曾在巴黎家居展上发布，结合了水曲柳、大理石和黄铜材料，它们的颜色和外形都不相同，达到了一种混合的平衡。而这次带来的桌子只有两种材料，以水曲柳作为长桌主体，上面增加了一块圆形或方形的小桌面，是黄铜材料或者大理石的，显得清爽很多，更实用。\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160607122307uXqelIs0kB9ZVzMJ.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.7603912\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160607122307XAlJKLcoMjC8r9T1.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.7603912\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160607122308ASpzm52gX9v6JNI8.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.98518519\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160607122308s918OmVQr62NUnoG.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.99537037\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<div>\r\n</div>\n\n\n"}